                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Channel Partners</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                            We've been recognised by Meta, Google, TikTok and Pinterest as their agency partners, so we're able to access Beta's and insights others can't.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 4: Creative (White) -->
                <div class="bg-white text-black p-8 rounded-[2rem] flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[320px]">
